column5: Does this madness ever end.... you Esox chasers out there???
I don't get it...bedroom halloween?  where would you hang them...ohhh ...never mind.
Great throw backs, Wayne. There's a few bucks there. Got enough large ZipLocs?
Didn't figure you'd ever use anything but a BumbleBee Believer again Wayne

Actually Roy...they're only $16US a pair, complete with one weight/hook per pair...from RedOctober Baits. I think my total there was $93 Cdn when I checked out on Paypal...and it stripped the shipping costs at check out as well. A dozen baits ... for the price of a Legend Plow!
Wayne is that the new phone lure for teenage Musky?
HAHAHA yep Dan...gets them young ones everytime. Some of the older female ones as well !!! LOL  Just a size comparison..phone is 8.5" long
Those ticklers are thick enough, you shouldn't catch anything.....  Nice colours too!
